The paper discusses planning techniques for autonomous systems, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The specific planning technique discussed is HTN planning, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the use of heuristics and encoding planning problems in other formalisms, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper presents an experimentation on a range of problems, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
